There are cvs instructions at 
http://people.redhat.com/davej
A link to cvsweb is also there.
Quick version number mapping, based on cvs annotate kernel-2.6.spec ..
2054 - 2.6.16-rc6-git3
2154 - 2.6.17.3
2174 - 2.6.17.8
